ye rɔt."

“Aca leec në kë ca leec,” acï Eli lueel.

Ɣɛn acï tak lɔn bï kek ya wënkääi ku nyankäi. Keek kaa rou ake nɔŋ nyïn cï gölic,
nhiɛ̈m col thöŋ, ku ɣeer, nyïn nhial-blue.

“Yïn ee raan yam,” acï Eli lueel, ke ɣa thɔ̈ɔ̈ŋ.

