“Yïn acï ɣötdiɛ̈ rum,” acï bɛ̈n lueel. “Acïï ŋic lɔn .
rac yen ee? Wolfbane acï piɔ̈ɔ̈c bï kɔc kuc thɔ̈ɔ̈r.”

